2. Purpose of Comments in HTML 
Purpose of Comments in HTML: 
● Comments are used to add notes or explanations in the code. ● They do not appear in the web browser. 
● Helpful for developers to understand the code. 
Example of Comments in HTML: 
<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html> 
<head> 
<title>Comments in HTML</title> 
</head> 
<body> 
<!-- This is a comment in HTML --> 
<h1>Welcome to My Website</h1> 
<p>This is a paragraph.</p> 
</body> 
</html>
